				<p class="headerDashlet"><strong>Glodyne- Reward &amp;
				Recognition Program</strong></p>
				<p class="blacklink" style="text-align: justify;">About: Individuals effort is a link for
				well being of business.. Saying thank you to those who help a
				company succeed can go a long way when members are sincere. Rewards
				and Recognition program are termed to value member s contributions
				and appreciate their efforts. Glodyne Rewards and Recognition
				(R&amp;R) is an annual employee recognition program. The reward
				strategy is initiated to reinforce efforts and reward the shining
				performers. The members are felicitated in Glofest - Glodyne
				annual event.</p>
				<p class="blacklink" style="text-align: justify;">Objective: Rewards and Recognition
				(R&amp;R) program spreads a power of positive ness among fellow
				members and gives a self recognition platform which helps to achieve
				set targets. Recognition culture motivates member to become more
				active in role assigned to them. The performers are identified on
				basis of various defined annual parameters.</p>
				<p class="headerDashlet"><strong>Awards category: </strong></p>
				<ol type="1" start="1">
					<li><span class="orange"><strong>Glodyne
					Superstar Award</strong></span>- <span class="blacklink" style="text-align: justify;">Superstar category
					recognize the talent who&nbsp;had&nbsp;shown&nbsp;outstanding
					performance during appraisal years April - March but had gone
					beyond the stated and implied expectations to display exemplary
					performance during the annual period. </span></li>
				</ol>
				<ol type="1" start="2">
					<li><u class="orange"><strong>Glodyne Rising star
					Award</strong></u>- <span class="blacklink" style="text-align: justify;">This award category
					identifies and recognize the talent who have
					displayed&nbsp;extraordinary performance during short&nbsp;period
					of six months. &nbsp; </span></li>
				</ol>
				<ol type="1" start="3">
					<li><u class="orange"><strong>Long Service Award</strong></u>-
					<span class="blacklink" style="text-align: justify;">Members identified for sharing long
					association with Glodyne for sharing there valuable contribution
					towards goals achieved.</span></li>
				</ol>
				<ol>
					<li><span class="orange"><strong>Persistent
					Five</strong></span>- <span class="blacklink" style="text-align: justify;">Recognition of exceptional
					services demonstrated for more than five years.&nbsp; </span></li>
					<li><span class="orange"><strong>Tenacious Ten</strong></span>-
					<span class="blacklink" style="text-align: justify;">Recognition of exceptional services
					demonstrated for more than Ten years.</span>&nbsp;</li>
				</ol>
				<p class="blacklink" style="text-align: justify;">Putting together a reward and recognition
				program is a great step toward improving employee morale and
				encouraging more productivity. Saying thank you to everyone for a
				job well done is important. A little  thank you  will go a long way!</p>
